Managed company go-to-market strategy for global expansion, increasing product revenue by 30%. Wrote technical and non-technical documentation for clients. Collected large quantities of raw drone data and managed the ML pipeline including preprocessing, training, and testing of multiple CNNs. {/* PlateIQ */} PlateIQ, Emeryville, CA Software Engineer (June 2018 - Sep 2018) Developed computer vision models for invoice layout type detection, and field localization achieving 91% accuracy. Managed and processed roughly labeled data from Mechanical Turk. Developed NLP error correction models, improving OCR system accuracy by 10%. {/* TextRecruit */} TextRecruit, San Jose, CA AI Engineer (Aug 2017 - Sep 2018) Developed chatbots for Human Resources using IBM Watson.
